terober.com/index.php?mod=io&op=getImg&&KYC\"\n                />\n                <span class=\"badge badge-sm badge-neutral mt-1\">中立捕猎</span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </td>\n          <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 text-left align-top\"></td>\n          <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 text-left align-top\"></td>\n          <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 text-left align-top\"></td>\n        </tr>\n\n        <!-- 第四个补给品（三个组件） -->\n        <tr>\n          <td\n            class=\"sticky left-0 z-10 border border-gray-300 p-2 text-center whitespace-nowrap\"\n          >\n            <label class=\"row-head\" title=\"切换：隐藏本行为空的整列\">\n              <input id=\"row-t-4\" type=\"checkbox\" class=\"row-toggle\" hidden />\n              <img\n                src=\"https://pic.whiterober.com/index.php?mod=io&op=getImg&&KYC\"\n              />\n            </label>\n          </td>\n          <td\n            class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 text-left align-top\"\n          >\n            英灵殿 | 龙舍 | 码头 〉维修箱<br />\n            <div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-1 items-start mb-3\">\n              <img\n                src=\"https://pic.whiterober.com/index.php?mod=io&op=getImg&&KYC\"\n              />\n            </div>\n          </td>\n          <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 text-left align-top\"></td>\n          <td\n            class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 text-left align-top\"\n          >\n            中央车站 | 焦土号 | 蛋糕岛〉维修箱<br />\n            <div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-1 items-start mb-3\">\n              <img\n                src=\"https://pic.whiterober.com/index.php?mod=io&op=getImg&&KYC\"\n              />\n            </div>\n          </td>\n          <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 text-left align-top\"></td>\n          <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 text-left align-top\"></td>\n        </tr>\n\n        <!-- 第五个补给品 -->\n        <tr>\n          <td\n            class=\"sticky left