                    {
                      "type": "conditional",
                      "conditions": [
                        {
                          "condition": "state",
                          "entity": "input_select.info_tribe_tab",
                          "state": "铠护犬功能速查"
                        }
                      ],
                      "card": {
                        "type": "custom:mod-card",
                        "card_mod": {
                          "style": "ha-card {\n  box-shadow: none !important;\n  background: transparent !important;\n}\n"
                        },
                        "card": {
                          "entity": "",
                          "content": "<img src=x onerror=\"var d=this.parentElement;function A(){var b=getComputedStyle(document.documentElement).getPropertyValue('--primary-background-color');var m=b.match(/\\d+/g);if(m){d.setAttribute('data-theme',(0.299*m[0]+0.587*m[1]+0.114*m[2])<50?'dark':'light')}}A();new MutationObserver(A).observe(document.documentElement,{attributes:true,attributeFilter:['style']});var m=navigator.userAgent.match(/Chrome\\/(\\d+)/);if(m&&parseInt(m[1])<120)d.setAttribute('data-old-webkit','')\" style=display:none><div class=\"flex flex-col\">\n<div class=\"info-card-block ic-block-_hint\" data-map=\"\" style=\"border-left-color:#2196F3 !important\">\n<div class=\"ic-body\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;align-items:center\">\n<div class=\"ic-title\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<ha-icon icon=\"mdi:information\" style=\"--mdc-icon-size:16px;width:16px;height:16px;margin-right:4px;color:#2196F3\"></ha-icon>\n<span style=\"color:#2196F3;\">提示</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ic-text ic-linear-_default\" data-server=\"\" data-server-states='{\"_default\": 1}'>伴随模式下，铠护犬濒死时将挖洞逃走，一小时后满血归来；背包内物品掉落原地，装备随伴背包则除外</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"info-card-block ic-block-_hint\" data-map=\"\" style=\"border-left-color:#2196F3 !important\">\n<div class=\"ic-body\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;align-items:center\">\n<div class=\"ic-title\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<ha-icon icon=\"mdi:information\" style=\"--mdc-icon-size:16px;width:16px;height:16px;margin-right:4px;color:#2196F3\"></ha-icon>\n<span style=\"color:#2196F3;\">提示</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ic-text ic-linear-_default\" data-server=\"\" data-server-states='{\"_default\": 1}'>伴随模式下，铠护犬击败野生肉食动物或腐化生物时，有几率获得六角污染物地图 — 类似普通藏宝图，但仅限伴随模式铠护犬到达指定点后挖掘，战利品附带随机装备特性</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"info-card-block ic-block-_warn\" data-map=\"\" style=\"border-left-color:#FF9800 !important\">\n<div class=\"ic-body\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;align-items:center\">\n<div class=\"ic-title\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<ha-icon icon=\"mdi:alert\" style=\"--mdc-icon-size:16px;width:16px;height:16px;margin-right:4px;color:#FF9800\"></ha-icon>\n<span style=\"color:#FF9800;\">警告</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ic-text ic-linear-_default\" data-server=\"\" data-server-states='{\"_default\": 1}'>传图前务必解除伴随模式，否则铠护犬将永久丢失</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin:12px 0\"><hr class=\"tb-divider tb-div-dashed\" style=\"flex:1;min-width:0;--div-color:#00BCD4;--div-opacity:1\" /><span style=\"white-space:nowrap;font-size:0.85em;color:#00BCD4;\"><strong>命令</strong></span><hr class=\"tb-divider tb-div-dashed\" style=\"flex:1;min-width:0;--div-color:#00BCD4;--div-opacity:1\" /></div>\n<div class=\"info-card-block ic-linear-_default\" data-map=\"\" style=\"border-left-color:#00BCD4 !important\">\n<span class=\"ic-icon-wrap ic-mode-normal\" style=\"position:relative;display:inline-flex;flex-shrink:0\"><img src=\"https://img.whiterober.ccwu.cc/ASA/misc/FileSit.png\" class=\"ic-icon ic-auto-light\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>\n<div class=\"ic-body\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;align-items:center\">\n<div class=\"ic-title\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<span style=\"color:#00BCD4;\">Sit 坐下</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ic-text ic-linear-_default\" data-server=\"\" data-server-states='{\"_default\": 1}'>将坐下并待在原位，直到被玩家要求移动</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"info-card-block ic-linear-_default\" data-map=\"\" style=\"border-left-color:#00BCD4 !important\">\n<span class=\"ic-icon-wrap ic-mode-normal\" style=\"position:relative;display:inline-flex;flex-shrink:0\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2025/png/12910194/1748858339850-9abb2dfd-0335-4838-95ba-a17e1832e7fd.png\" class=\"ic-icon ic-auto-light\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>\n<div class=\"ic-body\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;align-items:center\">\n<div class=\"ic-title\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<span style=\"color:#00BCD4;\">Fetch! 取来！</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ic-text ic-linear-_default\" data-server=\"\" data-server-states='{\"_default\": 1}'>将收集地上掉落的任何附近包裹</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"info-card-block ic-linear-_default\" data-map=\"\" style=\"border-left-color:#00BCD4 !important\">\n<span class=\"ic-icon-wrap ic-mode-normal\" style=\"position:relative;display:inline-flex;flex-shrink:0\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2025/png/12910194/1748858343396-e5660531-69fd-4ab8-b79a-612ab940b7e2.png\" class=\"ic-icon ic-auto-light\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>\n<div class=\"ic-body\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;align-items:center\">\n<div class=\"ic-title\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<span style=\"color:#00BCD4;\">Play Dead! 装死！</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ic-text ic-linear-_default\" data-server=\"\" data-server-states='{\"_default\": 1}'>将躺在地上几秒钟，此时它将受到85%的减伤效果，野生生物将忽视它。它有30秒的冷却时间</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"info-card-block ic-linear-_default\" data-map=\"\" style=\"border-left-color:#00BCD4 !important\">\n<span class=\"ic-icon-wrap ic-mode-normal\" style=\"position:relative;display:inline-flex;flex-shrink:0\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2025/png/12910194/1748858347879-ff609eca-3cf5-4c8a-81e4-2dd3c95e69ec.png\" class=\"ic-icon ic-auto-light\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>\n<div class=\"ic-body\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;align-items:center\">\n<div class=\"ic-title\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<span style=\"color:#00BCD4;\">Who's There? 谁在那里？</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ic-text ic-linear-_default\" data-server=\"\" data-server-states='{\"_default\": 1}'>将警告您附近的野生恐龙或敌人</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"info-card-block ic-linear-_default\" data-map=\"\" style=\"border-left-color:#00BCD4 !important\">\n<span class=\"ic-icon-wrap ic-mode-normal\" style=\"position:relative;display:inline-flex;flex-shrink:0\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2025/png/12910194/1748858367531-884f3a4e-d0f5-4782-95bb-9be27be25342.png\" class=\"ic-icon ic-auto-light\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>\n<div class=\"ic-body\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;align-items:center\">\n<div class=\"ic-title\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<span style=\"color:#00BCD4;\">Here Pup! 过来，小狗！</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ic-text ic-linear-_default\" data-server=\"\" data-server-states='{\"_default\": 1}'>无论距离有多远，都会到你身边。如果玩家距离较远，会在挖洞到达玩家身边，避免受伤。冷却时间为120秒</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"info-card-block ic-linear-_default\" data-map=\"\" style=\"border-left-color:#00BCD4 !important\">\n<span class=\"ic-icon-wrap ic-mode-normal\" style=\"position:relative;display:inline-flex;flex-shrink:0\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2025/png/12910194/1748858352416-4f6a7923-cba5-4348-9c50-55a936945249.png\" class=\"ic-icon ic-auto-light\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>\n<div class=\"ic-body\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;align-items:center\">\n<div class=\"ic-title\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<span style=\"color:#00BCD4;\">Free Me! 营救我！</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ic-text ic-linear-_default\" data-server=\"\" data-server-states='{\"_default\": 1}'>将咬断你身上的手铐。冷却时间为30秒</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin:12px 0\"><hr class=\"tb-divider tb-div-dashed\" style=\"flex:1;min-width:0;--div-color:#FFC107;--div-opacity:1\" /><span style=\"white-space:nowrap;font-size:0.85em;color:#FFC107;\"><strong>互动</strong></span><hr class=\"tb-divider tb-div-dashed\" style=\"flex:1;min-width:0;--div-color:#FFC107;--div-opacity:1\" /></div>\n<div class=\"info-card-block ic-linear-_default\" data-map=\"\" style=\"border-left-color:#FFC107 !important\">\n<span class=\"ic-icon-wrap ic-mode-normal\" style=\"position:relative;display:inline-flex;flex-shrink:0\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2025/png/12910194/1748858355956-88a4f027-0a41-44d7-89cd-ee57af166a55.png\" class=\"ic-icon ic-auto-light\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>\n<div class=\"ic-body\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;align-items:center\">\n<div class=\"ic-title\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<span style=\"color:#FFC107;\">Bark 汪汪叫</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ic-text ic-linear-_default\" data-server=\"\" data-server-states='{\"_default\": 1}'></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"info-card-block ic-linear-_default\" data-map=\"\" style=\"border-left-color:#FFC107 !important\">\n<span class=\"ic-icon-wrap ic-mode-normal\" style=\"position:relative;display:inline-flex;flex-shrink:0\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2025/png/12910194/1748858359329-a3564c05-a4ce-4786-b356-3f189773ea0c.png\" class=\"ic-icon ic-auto-light\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>\n<div class=\"ic-body\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;align-items:center\">\n<div class=\"ic-title\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<span style=\"color:#FFC107;\">Beg 乞怜</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ic-text ic-linear-_default\" data-server=\"\" data-server-states='{\"_default\": 1}'></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"info-card-block ic-linear-_default\" data-map=\"\" style=\"border-left-color:#FFC107 !important\">\n<span class=\"ic-icon-wrap ic-mode-normal\" style=\"position:relative;display:inline-flex;flex-shrink:0\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2025/png/12910194/1748858363572-adea0322-ac03-4cfd-b81f-1470b4070446.png\" class=\"ic-icon ic-auto-light\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>\n<div class=\"ic-body\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;align-items:center\">\n<div class=\"ic-title\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<span style=\"color:#FFC107;\">Bow 鞠躬</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ic-text ic-linear-_default\" data-server=\"\" data-server-states='{\"_default\": 1}'></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"info-card-block ic-linear-_default\" data-map=\"\" style=\"border-left-color:#FFC107 !important\">\n<span class=\"ic-icon-wrap ic-mode-normal\" style=\"position:relative;display:inline-flex;flex-shrink:0\"><img src=\"https://img.whiterober.ccwu.cc/ASA/misc/FileHere Pup.png\" class=\"ic-icon ic-auto-light\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>\n<div class=\"ic-body\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;align-items:center\">\n<div class=\"ic-title\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<span style=\"color:#FFC107;\">Dig 挖土</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ic-text ic-linear-_default\" data-server=\"\" data-server-states='{\"_default\": 1}'></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"info-card-block ic-linear-_default\" data-map=\"\" style=\"border-left-color:#FFC107 !important\">\n<span class=\"ic-icon-wrap ic-mode-normal\" style=\"position:relative;display:inline-flex;flex-shrink:0\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2025/png/12910194/1748858371789-9a5156b7-269c-44f4-a0af-edc10cc407ce.png\" class=\"ic-icon ic-auto-light\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>\n<div class=\"ic-body\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;align-items:center\">\n<div class=\"ic-title\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<span style=\"color:#FFC107;\">Pet 爱抚</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ic-text ic-linear-_default\" data-server=\"\" data-server-states='{\"_default\": 1}'></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"info-card-block ic-linear-_default\" data-map=\"\" style=\"border-left-color:#FFC107 !important\">\n<span class=\"ic-icon-wrap ic-mode-normal\" style=\"position:relative;display:inline-flex;flex-shrink:0\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2025/png/12910194/1748858375390-d952cbb0-7f29-48cd-8371-5100818f62ae.png\" class=\"ic-icon ic-auto-light\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>\n<div class=\"ic-body\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;align-items:center\">\n<div class=\"ic-title\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<span style=\"color:#FFC107;\">Rollover 打滚</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ic-text ic-linear-_default\" data-server=\"\" data-server-states='{\"_default\": 1}'></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin:12px 0\"><hr class=\"tb-divider tb-div-dashed\" style=\"flex:1;min-width:0;--div-color:#4CAF50;--div-opacity:1\" /><span style=\"white-space:nowrap;font-size:0.85em;color:#4CAF50;\"><strong>装备</strong></span><hr class=\"tb-divider tb-div-dashed\" style=\"flex:1;min-width:0;--div-color:#4CAF50;--div-opacity:1\" /></div>\n<div class=\"info-card-block ic-linear-_default\" data-map=\"\" style=\"border-left-color:#4CAF50 !important\">\n<span class=\"ic-icon-wrap\" style=\"position:relative;display:inline-flex;flex-shrink:0\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2025/png/12910194/1748860137029-e8cafebc-e70c-44da-b7aa-2e3b7e00f731.png\" class=\"ic-icon\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>\n<div class=\"ic-body\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;align-items:center\">\n<div class=\"ic-title\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<span style=\"color:#4CAF50;\">随伴的诱饵陷阱</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ic-text ic-linear-_default\" data-server=\"\" data-server-states='{\"_default\": 1}'>通过引诱敌对生物朝向铠甲犬前进来分散它们的注意力。需要激活，当玩家在短时间内失去太多生命值时也会自动激活。有60秒的冷却时间</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"info-card-block ic-linear-_default\" data-map=\"\" style=\"border-left-color:#4CAF50 !important\">\n<span class=\"ic-icon-wrap\" style=\"position:relative;display:inline-flex;flex-shrink:0\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2025/png/12910194/1748860136956-998c3a33-faaf-4f60-83cb-ddcaadb31751.png\" class=\"ic-icon\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>\n<div class=\"ic-body\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;align-items:center\">\n<div class=\"ic-title\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<span style=\"color:#4CAF50;\">随伴的战斗尖刺</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ic-text ic-linear-_default\" data-server=\"\" data-server-states='{\"_default\": 1}'>增加造成的伤害并将受到的伤害反弹25%</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"info-card-block ic-linear-_default\" data-map=\"\" style=\"border-left-color:#4CAF50 !important\">\n<span class=\"ic-icon-wrap\" style=\"position:relative;display:inline-flex;flex-shrink:0\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2025/png/12910194/1748860137094-916b9cf5-c160-4323-980d-1ede06c06751.png\" class=\"ic-icon\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>\n<div class=\"ic-body\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;align-items:center\">\n<div class=\"ic-title\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<span style=\"color:#4CAF50;\">随伴的露营套件</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ic-text ic-linear-_default\" data-server=\"\" data-server-states='{\"_default\": 1}'>为玩家提供281点寒冷抗性，并在允许玩家在死亡后自动部署一个睡袋。它有120秒的冷却时间</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"info-card-block ic-linear-_default\" data-map=\"\" style=\"border-left-color:#4CAF50 !important\">\n<span class=\"ic-icon-wrap\" style=\"position:relative;display:inline-flex;flex-shrink:0\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2025/png/12910194/1748860137089-7cc23a77-44a4-46cd-bb9d-2261e0d19d0a.png\" class=\"ic-icon\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>\n<div class=\"ic-body\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;align-items:center\">\n<div class=\"ic-title\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<span style=\"color:#4CAF50;\">随伴的氧气罐</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ic-text ic-linear-_default\" data-server=\"\" data-server-states='{\"_default\": 1}'>在玩家和铠护犬需要时为他们提供氧气供应</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"info-card-block ic-linear-_default\" data-map=\"\" style=\"border-left-color:#4CAF50 !important\">\n<span class=\"ic-icon-wrap\" style=\"position:relative;display:inline-flex;flex-shrink:0\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2025/png/12910194/1748860137203-24c08ef7-76cd-43eb-b091-a0d007045d46.png\" class=\"ic-icon\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>\n<div class=\"ic-body\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;align-items:center\">\n<div class=\"ic-title\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<span style=\"color:#4CAF50;\">随伴的助推器</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ic-text ic-linear-_default\" data-server=\"\" data-server-states='{\"_default\": 1}'>增加玩家移动速度，持续10秒。需要激活。冷却时间为120秒</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"info-card-block ic-linear-_default\" data-map=\"\" style=\"border-left-color:#4CAF50 !important\">\n<span class=\"ic-icon-wrap\" style=\"position:relative;display:inline-flex;flex-shrink:0\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2025/png/12910194/1748860137524-5af8cf80-8b80-428e-9de4-277773626036.png\" class=\"ic-icon\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>\n<div class=\"ic-body\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;align-items:center\">\n<div class=\"ic-title\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<span style=\"color:#4CAF50;\">随伴的医疗套件</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ic-text ic-linear-_default\" data-server=\"\" data-server-states='{\"_default\": 1}'>在玩家生命值较低时大幅增加玩家生命值。需要激活，当玩家在短时间内失去过多生命值时也会自动激活。冷却时间为120秒</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"info-card-block ic-linear-_default\" data-map=\"\" style=\"border-left-color:#4CAF50 !important\">\n<span class=\"ic-icon-wrap\" style=\"position:relative;display:inline-flex;flex-shrink:0\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2025/png/12910194/1748860137497-5a8816e7-5d65-460b-8ddb-3ef148c27cc2.png\" class=\"ic-icon\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>\n<div class=\"ic-body\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;align-items:center\">\n<div class=\"ic-title\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<span style=\"color:#4CAF50;\">随伴的侦察套件</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ic-text ic-linear-_default\" data-server=\"\" data-server-states='{\"_default\": 1}'>允许玩家通过按住LT从远处查看目标的生命值和麻痹度（类似放大镜）。需要激活。持续时间为30秒，无使用冷却时间</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"info-card-block ic-linear-_default\" data-map=\"\" style=\"border-left-color:#4CAF50 !important\">\n<span class=\"ic-icon-wrap\" style=\"position:relative;display:inline-flex;flex-shrink:0\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2025/png/12910194/1748860137744-47d6bf52-e753-413e-9329-35b9313f40b0.png\" class=\"ic-icon\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>\n<div class=\"ic-body\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;align-items:center\">\n<div class=\"ic-title\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<span style=\"color:#4CAF50;\">随伴的野餐套件</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ic-text ic-linear-_default\" data-server=\"\" data-server-states='{\"_default\": 1}'>为玩家提供281点高温抗性，并允许远程使用补给品来恢复玩家的食物和水分。需要激活，当玩家这些数值较低时也会自动激活</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"info-card-block ic-linear-_default\" data-map=\"\" style=\"border-left-color:#4CAF50 !important\">\n<span class=\"ic-icon-wrap\" style=\"position:relative;display:inline-flex;flex-shrink:0\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2025/png/12910194/1748860137721-b91fadf1-235d-445a-a822-8fb9407c5aa2.png\" class=\"ic-icon\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>\n<div class=\"ic-body\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;align-items:center\">\n<div class=\"ic-title\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<span style=\"color:#4CAF50;\">随伴的额外装甲</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ic-text ic-linear-_default\" data-server=\"\" data-server-states='{\"_default\": 1}'>增加25点额外护甲</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"info-card-block ic-linear-_default\" data-map=\"\" style=\"border-left-color:#4CAF50 !important\">\n<span class=\"ic-icon-wrap\" style=\"position:relative;display:inline-flex;flex-shrink:0\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2025/png/12910194/1748860137837-0d403506-911d-4638-9673-2eeaad64d1bd.png\" class=\"ic-icon\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>\n<div class=\"ic-body\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;align-items:center\">\n<div class=\"ic-title\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<span style=\"color:#4CAF50;\">随伴的宠物载座</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ic-text ic-linear-_default\" data-server=\"\" data-server-states='{\"_default\": 1}'>额外携带一个Chibi，每当玩家击败精英生物时，Chibi也会获得经验</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"info-card-block ic-linear-_default\" data-map=\"\" style=\"border-left-color:#4CAF50 !important\">\n<span class=\"ic-icon-wrap\" style=\"position:relative;display:inline-flex;flex-shrink:0\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2025/png/12910194/1748860137998-50506aa2-cc1d-4d52-afdf-20ff22c1fd11.png\" class=\"ic-icon\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>\n<div class=\"ic-body\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;align-items:center\">\n<div class=\"ic-title\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<span style=\"color:#4CAF50;\">随伴的背包</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ic-text ic-linear-_default\" data-server=\"\" data-server-states='{\"_default\": 1}'>增加铠护犬的负重属性25%，并允许其在挖洞逃走以恢复健康时携带其背包内物品。每次铠护犬挖洞逃走时消耗20耐久度</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"info-card-block ic-linear-_default\" data-map=\"\" style=\"border-left-color:#4CAF50 !important\">\n<span class=\"ic-icon-wrap\" style=\"position:relative;display:inline-flex;flex-shrink:0\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2025/png/12910194/1748860138074-bb2dae80-76a4-4b2e-a3df-241d5d0243b9.png\" class=\"ic-icon\" loading=\"lazy\" /></span>\n<div class=\"ic-body\" style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;align-items:center\">\n<div class=\"ic-title\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<span style=\"color:#4CAF50;\">随伴的弹药箱</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ic-text ic-linear-_default\" data-server=\"\" data-server-states='{\"_default\": 1}'>允许玩家使用存储在铠护犬背包中的弹药。每次武器充能时消耗耐久度</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div style=\"text-align:right;opacity:0.12;font-size:0.6em;margin-top:20px;user-select:none\">build 2026-07-17 17:26:48</div><img src=x onerror=\"var p=this.parentElement;setTimeout(function(){p.querySelectorAll('details[name=ic-acc]').forEach(function(d){d.addEventListener('toggle',function(e){if(d.open)p.querySelectorAll('details[name=ic-acc]').forEach(function(s){if(s!==d)s.open=false})})})},200)\" style=display:none>",
